{"tid":2388571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飛鵝山12名行山客電筒照車內情侶 違限聚令收告票","createTime":"2021-01-31T08:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T10:57:03.000Z","uid":66271,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0c94824b7a1a4346f80c167f3c7d67abcddcbe87","tid":2388571,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/01/2021013108335824637_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F01%2F2021013108335824637_FB.jpg&h=8bf4a0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛鵝山一對20多歲情侶凌晨在私家車內聊天期間，懷疑被12名行夜山的男女以電筒照射滋擾，於是報警求助。警方到場調查後，向12名行山客發出違反「限聚令」告票，每人罰款5000元。<br />\n<br />\n事發於凌晨零時左右，一名28歲男子與其24歲女友在泊於黄大仙飛鵝山道近山頂位置的私家車內聊天。<br />\n<br />\n期間有12名行夜山的男女途經，有人走近懷疑以電筒照射車內，情侶不滿遭冒犯，於是下車與對方理論，兩方發生口角，情侶報警聲稱遇襲。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場經初步調查後，將案件列糾紛處理，而涉案年齡介乎24至46歲的9男3女行山客，則涉嫌違反「限聚令」，警員向他們發出告票，每人罰款5000元。"},{"pid":"e5ed13bfe30a899d1d24005bfdbe92e6a01a1fcf","tid":2388571,"uid":223084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"阻人車震扑嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fae3cde9ede133b975ff123d8be0db1a848a635","tid":2388571,"uid":99973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"阻人仆野比人燒春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2169c5aa481cd5ef75762f7f57b0fe844245392f","tid":2388571,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset